'''Sony Xperia X'''是[[索尼|索尼]]於2016年2月22日在MWC發表的手機，同時發佈了同為X系列的[[Sony_Xperia_XA|Sony Xperia XA]]。XA搭載5吋螢幕、MediaTek helio™ P10處理器、2GB記憶體、搭载全新1300万像素Exmor RS相机模组，支持混合对焦，激光自动对焦。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJynMD |title=SONY Odin冠名Xperia X 将于CES或MWC 2013上露面 |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230001218/https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJynMD }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJVLP6 |title=索尼XPERIA X港版价格公布 最低2298港币 |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230001219/https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJVLP6 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.cgtn.com/news/31556a4d35677a6333566d54/share_p.html |title=Sony pins hopes on 4K video to revive smartphone sales |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230002346/https://news.cgtn.com/news/31556a4d35677a6333566d54/share_p.html }}</ref>

== 设计 ==
新一代抛弃了之前采用的全平衡设计，改用全新的Unified Design(合一设计)，使用了2.5D第4代的康宁大猩猩玻璃作为前面板，并且此次不支持防尘防水。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2017-10/28/content_33807979.htm |title=Sony puts new technologies on display - Business - Chinadaily.com.cn |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230002356/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2017-10/28/content_33807979.htm }}</ref>

